# Developer Agent Context Summary

## Last Run: 2026-03-16

## Completed Work This Session

### Project: signet — All 5 phases (Tasks #874-878)
TypeScript drop-in replacement for object-hash (~31-41M weekly npm downloads). Zero runtime dependencies, Node.js 18+, ESM+CJS dual build.

Core: Deterministic serializer byte-identical to object-hash v3.0.0. All JS types: string, number, boolean, null, undefined, bigint, symbol, Date, RegExp, Error, URL, Set, Map, Buffer, TypedArrays (Uint8/Int8/Uint16/Int16/Uint32/Int32/Float32/Float64/Uint8Clamped), ArrayBuffer, functions, objects. Circular reference detection via context array. Options: excludeKeys, excludeValues, ignoreUnknown, respectType, respectFunctionNames, respectFunctionProperties, unorderedArrays, unorderedSets, unorderedObjects, replacer.

Hasher: sha1/sha256/sha512/md5/passthrough algorithms, hex/base64/buffer/binary encodings via Node crypto.

API: default hash(), hash.sha1(), hash.MD5(), hash.keys(), hash.keysMD5(), hash.writeToStream(). Compat layer at signet/compat/object-hash.

161 tests across 3 test files. 5 commits pushed to agentine/signet. CI green on Node 20+22. MIT license.

